<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    <b>OttWatch</b> is dedicated to making it easier to be part of the political conversation in Ottawa.<br/>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-6">
    This is "version2" of OttWatch. Check out <a href="http://ottwatch.ca">version 1</a> which has a lot
    more content available. Version 2 will continue to grow in scope, as time allows.
  </div>
</div>

<div style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
  <h1>Recent announcements</h1>
</div>
<div class="owrows">
<% @announcements.each do |a| %>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <%= link_to(a.link_to_context, a.link_to_reference) %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <%= a.message %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2" style="text-align: right;">
      <%= a.created_at.in_time_zone("America/New_York").strftime("%Y-%m-%d") %>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>
</div>

<div style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
  <a id="about"></a>
  <h1>About/Contact</h1>
</div>

Twitter: @ottwatch or @kevinodotnet